1. *Slugi*, donesi mi vodu. (Servant, bring me some water.)
2. Bio je *sluga* kod bogatih ljudi. (He was a servant at rich people's houses.)
3. Zbog svog *sluganstva*, nije mogao da dođe na vreme. (Due to his servitude, he couldn't come on time.)
4. U nekim zemljama, *sluga* se smatra kao posao za žene. (In some countries, being a servant is considered a job for women.)
5. *Sluge* su bili obučeni u uniforme. (The servants were dressed in uniforms.)
6. On je *sluga* svog poslodavca. (He is his employer's servant.)
7. U srednjem veku, *sluga* je bio podređeni u feudalnom društvu. (In the Middle Ages, a servant was a subordinate in feudal society.)
8. *Sluga* je otišao po hranu za gospodara. (The servant went to get food for the master.)
9. Život *sluga* može biti veoma težak. (A servant's life can be very difficult.)
10. *Sluge* su često bili loše plaćeni. (Servants were often poorly paid.)